{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Cookie","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Cookie","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Cookie 是一個網站通過瀏覽器訪問在訪客電腦裏留下的一小段信息。</p>\n<p>Cookies 被網站用於個性化用戶個人的網頁體驗。訪問該網站時它可能覆蓋了用戶的喜好或輸入。用戶可以自定義他們的瀏覽器是個接受或是刪除 cookies.</p>\n<p>Cookies 可以設置和修改，在伺服器級別使用<code>Set-Cookie</code> <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTTP/Cookies\">HTTP header</a>, 或在 JavaScript 使用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/cookie\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">document.cookie (en-US)</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基礎知識","title":"基礎知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科上的 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTTP_cookie\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTTP cookie</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"Cookie 是一個網站通過瀏覽器訪問在訪客電腦裏留下的一小段信息。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Cookie","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/cookie","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/cookie/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Cookie","title":"Cookie"}],"pageTitle":"Cookie - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}